from rest_framework import serializers

from django.urls import resolve

from products.models import Product, Tag, ProductVariant, ProductVariantOption, ProductVariantOptionValue, ProductImage, VariantImageMapping

from categories.models import Category

from shops.models import Shop, DeliveryZone, Country

from django.contrib.auth import get_user_model


class UserSerializer(serializers.ModelSerializer):

class Meta:

model = get_user_model()

fields = ['id', 'username', 'email', 'mobile', 'user_bio', 'is_active']

read_only_fields = ['is_active']

extra_kwargs = {

'url': {'view_name': 'user-detail', 'lookup_field': 'pk'}

}


class TagSerializer(serializers.HyperlinkedModelSerializer):

class Meta:

model = Tag

fields = '__all__'

extra_kwargs = {

'url': {'view_name': 'tag-detail', 'lookup_field': 'pk'}

}


class CategorySerializer(serializers.HyperlinkedModelSerializer):

class Meta:

model = Category

fields = '__all__'

extra_kwargs = {

'url': {'view_name': 'category-detail', 'lookup_field': 'pk'}

}


class CountrySerializer(serializers.HyperlinkedModelSerializer):

class Meta:

model = Country

fields = '__all__'

extra_kwargs = {

'url': {'view_name': 'country-detail', 'lookup_field': 'pk'}

}


class DeliveryZoneSerializer(serializers.HyperlinkedModelSerializer):

countries = CountrySerializer(many=True, read_only=True)

class Meta:

model = DeliveryZone

fields = '__all__'

extra_kwargs = {

'url': {'view_name': 'deliveryzone-detail', 'lookup_field': 'pk'}

}


class ShopSerializer(serializers.ModelSerializer):

class Meta:

model = Shop

fields = '__all__'


class ProductImageSerializer(serializers.HyperlinkedModelSerializer):

id = serializers.ReadOnlyField()

class Meta:

model = ProductImage

fields = '__all__'

extra_kwargs = {

'url': {'view_name': 'productimage-detail', 'lookup_field': 'pk'}

}


class ProductVariantOptionValueSerializer(serializers.ModelSerializer):

class Meta:

model = ProductVariantOptionValue

fields = ('value', 'option')


class ProductVariantOptionSerializer(serializers.ModelSerializer):

id = serializers.IntegerField(source='pk', read_only=True) # Define the id field explicitly

values = ProductVariantOptionValueSerializer(many=True, read_only=True)


class Meta:

model = ProductVariantOption

fields = ('id', 'name', 'values')


class VariantImageMappingSerializer(serializers.ModelSerializer):

class Meta:

model = VariantImageMapping

fields = ('variant', 'image')


class ProductVariantSerializer(serializers.ModelSerializer):

option_values = ProductVariantOptionValueSerializer(many=True)

image_mappings = VariantImageMappingSerializer(many=True, read_only=True)

product = serializers.PrimaryKeyRelatedField(queryset=Product.objects.all())


class Meta:

model = ProductVariant

fields = ('id', 'option_values', 'image_mappings', 'product', 'price', 'quantity', 'is_active')


def create(self, validated_data):

option_values_data = validated_data.pop('option_values')

variant = ProductVariant.objects.create(**validated_data)


option_values = []

for ov_data in option_values_data:

option = ProductVariantOption.objects.get(pk=ov_data['option'].pk)

option_value, _ = ProductVariantOptionValue.objects.get_or_create(value=ov_data['value'], option=option)

option_values.append(option_value)


variant.option_values.set(option_values)

return variant



class ProductSerializer(serializers.HyperlinkedModelSerializer):

id = serializers.ReadOnlyField()

tags = TagSerializer(many=True, read_only=True)

variants = ProductVariantSerializer(many=True, read_only=True)

images = ProductImageSerializer(many=True, read_only=True)

delivery_zone = DeliveryZoneSerializer(read_only=True)

user = serializers.HiddenField(default=serializers.CurrentUserDefault())

uploaded_images = serializers.ListField(

child=serializers.ImageField(allow_empty_file=False, use_url=False),

write_only=True

title: Ergonomic Adjustable Laptop Stand For Desks & Home Office
description:
About this item

  • 6-level adjustable laptop stand for desk
  • Stylish aluminum construction
  • Anti-slip padding on the stand
  • Handles laptops (7-15 inch), Macbooks, tablets, mobiles
  • Foldable laptop stand for easy storage
  • Open-cut design for proper ventilation
  • Lightweight


Item description from the seller

Reduce back and eye strain with this ergonomic adjustable laptop stand that offers a sturdy triangular configuration for handling almost every laptop. The stand comes with incline increments and anti-slip surface pads along with a ventilation design so you can keep your devices on the stand for as long as you want.

Work on your presentations or binge-watch your favorite TV shows, conduct lengthy zoom sessions or FaceTime your loved ones for hours - this home and office laptop stand will come in handy in all situations. 

What youll get:


  • Reduce pains: Extended use of laptops and electronic devices have resulted in increasing cases of neck, eye, back pain, and poor posture. This ergonomic laptop stand will keep your vertebrae straight and prevent back, neck and eye strain as well.
  • Sturdy aluminum built: Made of lightweight yet strong, sturdy aluminum, it is there to stay with you for long.
  • Stable triangular design: The linkages of the adjustable laptop stand are arranged in a triangular configuration to provide maximum stability.
  • 6-incline points: Change the height of your laptop from 100-160mm according to your need. It is an ideal stand for desk and for bed. 
  • Anti-slip padding: The stand comes with full anti-skid padding on the linkages along with 2 holding mounts, so its never displaced.
  • Design for ventilation: Comes with an open design that allows ventilation for your device. Your laptop or tablet will never get overheated. Enjoy max speed & performance.
  • Folding design for easy storage: The compact design of the ergonomic laptop stand allows it to be highly portable. Carry it anywhere with you; to the office, while driving, on international trips, etc.
  • Compatible with all devices: Works with laptops (7-15 inch), tablets, mobiles, MacBooks.

description:
product test 1 description

You surely know how crucial it is to always have your laptop, mouse, and charger with you if you’re a digital worker.

But carrying a laptop along with all its appliances is challenging. That’s why you often miss out on any laptop’s appliance at home or at work, which can decrease your efficiency.

So, put an end to this problem and work relaxedly with this Multifunctional Laptop Bag.

It’s handy to bring anywhere and has built-in a variety of accessories that make it simple to set up your entire workstation wherever you choose, this laptop bag is perfect for both remote and office work.

What you’ll get:

  • Fast laptop portability: This bag is handy to bring your laptop wherever you go. Put your system in it and work anywhere you like without hassle. 
  • 100% laptop protection: Refined leather resists scratches and is waterproof. Don’t be stressed about your laptop in case it’s raining and you’re outside or on a bike.
  • Ergonomic kickstand: This bag is equipped with a well-designed kickstand. It sets your laptop in the perfect direction to provide a feasible working angle. In addition, if you use your system for long hours, it protects you from neck muscles soreness and backache.
  • Multiple laptop appliances: Mouse pad and pen slot are built in this laptop bag to make you pleasantly use the system wherever you desire. Mouse and charger pouch are also included in the package to help you carry laptop essentials anywhere.
  • Wide applications: This laptop bag is ideal for Apple Macbook, Dell, HP, and more. Simply check your laptop size and order the bag accordingly.
